ze_zombie_factory

Map is made by Chiizi. This is my first released ze map.

INFO: Map has 4 difficulties, easy,medium,hard and extreme + level choosing round. Each difficulty have own different route. There are also two special weapons hidden in the map. Map contains "boss" fight at level hard and extreme, but the boss isn't very hard because map itself is pretty hard. There is 1 secret in the map that can be unlocked by finding all the hidden watermelons.

**UPDATES:**
- Added some small details
- Boss is now harder
- Map looks better now
- I made some changes at holding points and routes
- Special item buff

!!!YOU ARE NOT ALLOWED TO DECOMPILE THIS MAP OR USE ITS CUSTOM MATERIALS WITHOUT CHIIZI'S PERMISSION!!!
